&gt;&gt;&gt; WHAT:  add new component to ompi/rte framework<br>
&gt;&gt;&gt;<br>
&gt;&gt;&gt; WHY:   because it will simplify our maintenance &amp; provide an alt. reference<br>
&gt;&gt;&gt;<br>
