&gt;&gt;&gt; support using OMPI with an alternate runtime system.  This will also<br>
&gt;&gt;&gt; provide an alternate component to ORTE, which was motivation for PMI<br>
&gt;&gt;&gt; component in related RFC.   We build/test nightly and it occasionally<br>
&gt;&gt;&gt; catches ompi-rte abstraction violations, etc.<br>
